# File Syntax

- Tabs as Spaces
- 2 space indentation for all files (TypeScript, JavaScript, CSS)
- 2 space indentation specifically for React components (.tsx files)
- 2 space indentation specifically for styles (.css files)
- No whitespace after last code character of the file
- End file with newline
- Consistent spacing around operators and after commas
- One blank line between logical sections
- No trailing whitespace in lines
- Maximum line length of 100 characters
